nna Thiel","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"the-worlds-best-nurse-gift-for-nurse","reply":"","reply_date":"","picture_urls":"","ip_address":"","location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"","body_zh_TW":"","body_cs":"","body_da":"","body_nl":"","body_fi":"","body_fr":"","body_de":"","body_el":"","body_he":"","body_it":"","body_ja":"","body_ko":"","body_ms":"","body_no":"","body_pl":"","body_pt":"","body_es":"","body_sv":"","body_th":"","status":"","user_identifier":""},{"title":"","body":"","rating":"5","review_date":"2/17/2019 0:24","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Carlie Weimann","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"the-worlds-best-nurse-gift-for-nurse","reply":"","reply_date":"","picture_urls":"","ip_address":"","location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"","body_zh_TW":"","body_cs":"","body_da":"","body_nl":"","body_fi":"","body_fr":"","body_de":"","body_el":"","body_he":"","body_it":"","body_ja":"","body_ko":"","body_ms":"","body_no":"","body_pl":"","body_pt":"","body_es":"","body_sv":"","body_th":"","status":"","user_identifier":""},{"title":"","body":"Great quality mug! I'm happy with the fast shipping on the order! Seller is always very nice & quick to answer all questions! Thank you!","rating":"5","review_date":"2/8/2019 7:22","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Andy Rempel","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"the-worlds-best-nurse-gift-for-nurse","reply":"","reply_date":"","picture_urls":"","ip_address":"","location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"كوب رائع الجودة! أنا سعيد بسرعة توصيل الطلب! البائع لطيف للغاية وسريع الاستجابة لجميع الأسئلة! شكرًا لك!","body_zh_TW":"馬克杯品質真棒！出貨速度也很快，我很滿意！賣家一直都很友善，回覆問題也很及時！謝謝！","body_cs":"Hrnek skvělé kvality! Jsem spokojený s rychlým dodáním objednávky! Prodejce je vždy velmi milý a rychle odpovídá na všechny otázky! Děkuji!","body_da":"Krus af god kvalitet! Jeg er tilfreds med den hurtige levering af ordren! Sælgeren er altid meget flink og hurtig til at besvare alle spørgsmål! Tak!","body_nl":"Mok van uitstekende kwaliteit! Ik ben erg blij met de snelle verzending! De verkoper is altijd erg aardig en beantwoordt al mijn vragen snel! Dankjewel!","body_fi":"Laadukas muki! Olen tyytyväinen tilauksen nopeaan toimitukseen! Myyjä on aina erittäin mukava ja vastaa nopeasti kaikkiin kysymyksiin! Kiitos!","body_fr":"Mug de très bonne qualité ! Je suis ravie de la rapidité de la livraison ! Le vendeur est toujours très aimable et répond rapidement à toutes les questions ! Merci !","body_de":"Tolle Tasse! Ich freue mich über die schnelle Lieferung! Der Verkäufer ist immer sehr nett und beantwortet alle Fragen prompt! Vielen Dank!","body_el":"Κούπα εξαιρετικής ποιότητας! Είμαι ευχαριστημένη με την γρήγορη αποστολή της παραγγελίας! Ο πωλητής είναι πάντα πολύ ευγενικός και γρήγορος να απαντήσει σε όλες τις ερωτήσεις! Ευχαριστώ!","body_he":"ספל באיכות מעולה! אני מרוצה מהמשלוח המהיר של ההזמנה! המוכר תמיד נחמד מאוד ועונה במהירות על כל השאלות! תודה!","body_it":"Tazza di ottima qualità! Sono contenta della spedizione veloce! Il venditore è sempre molto gentile e risponde rapidamente a tutte le domande! Grazie!","body_ja":"素晴らしい品質のマグカップです！注文から発送までの速さにも満足しています！出品者の方はいつもとても親切で、質問にも迅速に答えてくれます！ありがとうございます！","body_ko":"머그컵 품질이 정말 좋아요! 배송도 빨라서 만족합니다! 판매자분도 항상 친절하시고 질문에도 바로바로 답변해주셔서 감사합니다!","body_ms":"Mug berkualiti tinggi! Saya berpuas hati dengan penghantaran pesanan yang pantas! Penjual sentiasa sangat baik & pantas menjawab semua soalan! Terima kasih!","body_no":"Krus av høy kvalitet! Jeg er fornøyd med den raske leveringen av bestillingen! Selgeren er alltid veldig hyggelig og rask til å svare på alle spørsmål! Takk!","body_pl":"Kubek świetnej jakości! Jestem zadowolony z szybkiej wysyłki zamówienia! Sprzedawca jest zawsze bardzo miły i szybko odpowiada na wszystkie pytania! Dziękuję!","body_pt":"Caneca de ótima qualidade! Estou satisfeita com a rapidez da entrega! O vendedor é sempre muito atencioso e responde a todas as perguntas rapidamente! Obrigada!","body_es":"¡Taza de excelente calidad! ¡Estoy muy contento con la rapidez del envío! El vendedor siempre es muy amable y responde rápidamente a todas las preguntas. ¡Gracias!","body_sv":"Mugg av hög kvalitet! Jag är nöjd med den snabba leveransen av beställningen! Säljaren är alltid väldigt trevlig och snabb på att svara på alla frågor! Tack!","body_th":"แก้วคุณภาพดีเยี่ยม! ฉันพอใจกับการจัดส่งที่รวดเร็วมาก! ผู้ขายใจดีและตอบคำถามทุกข้ออย่างรวดเร็วเสมอ! ขอบคุณค่ะ!","status":"","user_identifier":""},{"title":"","body":"","rating":"5","review_date":"2/4/2019 8:18","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Edison Bogisich","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"the-worlds-best-nurse-gift-for-nurse","reply":"","reply_date":"","picture_urls":"","ip_address":"","location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"","body_zh_TW":"","body_cs":"","body_da":"","body_nl":"","body_fi":"","body_fr":"","body_de":"","body_el":"","body_he":"","body_it":"","body_ja":"","body_ko":"","body_ms":"","body_no":"","body_pl":"","body_pt":"","body_es":"","body_sv":"","body_th":"","status":"","user_identifier":""},{"title":"","body":"","rating":"5","review_date":"2/2/2019 1:57","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Herman Kertzmann","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"the-worlds-best-nurse-gift-for-nurse","reply":"","reply_date":"","picture_urls":"","ip_address":"","location":"","metaobject_handle":"","body_ar":"","body_zh_TW":"","body_cs":"","body_da":"","body_nl":"","body_fi":"","body_fr":"","body_de":"","body_el":"","body_he":"","body_it":"","body_ja":"","body_ko":"","body_ms":"","body_no":"","body_pl":"","body_pt":"","body_es":"","body_sv":"","body_th":"","status":"","user_identifier":""},{"title":"","body":"","rating":"5","review_date":"1/9/2019 9:18","source":"aliexpress","curated":"ok","reviewer_name":"Daphney Brown","reviewer_email":"","product_id":"","product_handle":"the-wo